august 23 , 30 bc ) , better known by the nicknames caesarion ( ; , kaisari≈çn , literally " little caesar " ; ) and ptolemy caesar ( ; , ptolemaios kaisar ; ) , was the last king of the ptolemaic dynasty of egypt , who reigned jointly with his mother cleopatra vii of egypt , from september 2 , 44 bc. he held the position of sole ruler between the death of cleopatra , on august 12 , 30 bc , up to august 23 , 30 bc , the time his death was ordered by octavian , who would become the roman emperor augustus .

